{"tid":1016891,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"妹夫包二奶留低一家三口 有咩方法逼佢比贍養費？","createTime":"2019-02-11T05:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T12:28:54.000Z","uid":123784,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"418f5e496e39db52ab0dbedb3af57f8048a11929","tid":1016891,"uid":123784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:17:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n個妹前半年生第二胎所以辭左份工諗注全職湊bb 疊埋心水等bb大到咁上下先番出黎做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但最近幾個月發現妹夫開始變左 開始收埋d錢唔比家用<br />\n係咁簽卡買女人野但又唔係送比我個妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我個妹梗係忍唔注查下佢啦<br />\n點知就發現佢番大陸出差個陣搭上左隻大陸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我妹夫一直出現金糧  依家踢爆左佢叫佢比贍養費<br />\n佢竟然同我個妹講： 你點告我都無用 我係唔會比錢既<br />\n佢呀媽仲話我個妹依家無收入 同我個妹搶兩個小朋友一定搶贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n想問下個人渣出現金糧 一個月搵五皮幾<br />\n有無方法可以逼到佢俾贍養費我個妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個妹依家真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家庭破碎<br />\n睇下依個人渣幾時比天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0030262412519e60e32bfd153bfd9b6b068c35","tid":1016891,"uid":65201,"like":3,"dislike":49,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:19:24.000Z","msg":"女人唔做野要問男人攞錢<br />\n男人唔比就要搞鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女權又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fe960a545a7ca49a1f2ab88d38739a74926a4a","tid":1016891,"uid":94828,"like":10,